{"prompt": "Generate a website for a community non-profit. The website should be dynamic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Community Connect</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #c1272d;\n            --secondary-color: #e0a3a5;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --header-text-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--header-text-color);\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 0.5rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 1rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 0 2rem;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            background: var(--background-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 3rem 1rem;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            color: var(--header-text-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            color: var(--header-text-color);\n            font-size: 2.8rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--header-text-color);\n            padding: 10px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            margin-top: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background: #991f24;\n        }\n\n        .gallery {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .gallery img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .gallery img:hover {\n            transform: scale(1.03);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--header-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        #contact-form label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n\n        #contact-form input[type=\"text\"],\n        #contact-form input[type=\"email\"],\n        #contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n\n        #contact-form button {\n            background: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--header-text-color);\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        #contact-form button:hover {\n            background: #991f24;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Community Connect</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#programs\">Our Programs</a>\n        <a href=\"#gallery\">Gallery</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact Us</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"hero\">\n            <h2>Building a Stronger Community Together</h2>\n            <p>Join us in making a positive impact in our neighborhood. Every contribution counts!</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get Involved Today</a>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Our Non-Profit</h2>\n            <p>Community Connect is dedicated to fostering a vibrant and supportive environment for all residents. We believe in the power of collaboration to create meaningful change and address local needs. Our mission is to empower individuals, strengthen families, and enhance the overall well-being of our community through various initiatives and programs.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"programs\">\n            <h2>Our Programs</h2>\n            <p>We offer a range of programs designed to serve different segments of our community:</p>\n            <ul>\n                <li><strong>Youth Mentorship:</strong> Guiding and supporting young individuals.</li>\n                <li><strong>Senior Support Services:</strong> Assisting our elderly population with various needs.</li>\n                <li><strong>Community Garden Projects:</strong> Promoting sustainable living and healthy eating.</li>\n                <li><strong>Local Event Sponsorship:</strong> Bringing people together for fun and engagement.</li>\n            </ul>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"gallery\">\n            <h2>Gallery of Impact</h2>\n            <div class=\"gallery\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/c1272d/ffffff?text=Event+1\" alt=\"Community Event 1\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/e0a3a5/333333?text=Volunteers\" alt=\"Volunteers in Action\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/c1272d/ffffff?text=Program+Activity\" alt=\"Program Activity\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/e0a3a5/333333?text=Community+Gathering\" alt=\"Community Gathering\">\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>We'd love to hear from you! Whether you want to volunteer, donate, or learn more about our work, please reach out.</p>\n            <form id=\"contact-form\">\n                <div>\n                    <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                    <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                    <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                    <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                    <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                    <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n                </div>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Community Connect. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contact-form').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Thank you for your message! We will be in touch soon.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}